title: Electricity consumption of large companies fell 0.1% in September (Red Eléctrica Corporación SA)
text: ( Source : Red Eléctrica Corporación SA) The electricity consumption of large and medium-sized companies fell 0.1% in September compared with the same month the previous year, according to data from the Red Eléctrica Index ( IRE ). Broken down
